snippet.textDisplay:
Here’s how you do the Mac and chees hot Cheeto with mozzarella:
Have big pot and make sure you put vegetable oil or olive oil

Then you make the Mac and cheese have a square cylinder and then put the Mac and cheese in there and the mozzarella stick in the middle let that freeze for maybe an hour (check on it now and then cause you don’t want it tooo frozen)

When that is frozen crush the Hot Cheetos then get flour and stir the egg well and then heat the nacho cheese and then put it in a ziplock bag when it’s a bit cool so I can easily drizzle on the food nicely and hopefully not melt the bag 😂 (pretty much using it like a frosting bag but for nacho cheese sauce)

Then when the Mac and cheese and mozzarella stick is frozen (hopefully) it should slide out the container then put that in your egg and then flour it a little then put all that Hot Cheeto dust on that
Put it in the “fryer” (which is your hot pot full of oil make sure to have like a spatula and what not or tongs) then drop that in there make sure it deep fries a little then see if it’s cooked not burn then (I recommend looking up a YouTube video to know how long deep fried food is cooked and all) then when thats done put the nacho cheese sauce in a corner then cut the corner drizzle it on the deep fried food and WALA it’s done 😋😂

Edit: I would recommend to look up the recipe online cause there is people who I believe made this if I remember but any who make sure you get measurements right and all and I think your set so enjoy 😂👌🏼

Have big pot and make sure you put vegetable oil or olive oil

Then you make the Mac and cheese have a square cylinder and then put the Mac and cheese in there and the mozzarella stick in the middle let that freeze for maybe an hour (check on it now and then cause you don’t want it tooo frozen)

When that is frozen crush the Hot Cheetos then get flour and stir the egg well and then heat the nacho cheese and then put it in a ziplock bag when it’s a bit cool so I can easily drizzle on the food nicely and hopefully not melt the bag 😂 (pretty much using it like a frosting bag but for nacho cheese sauce)

Then when the Mac and cheese and mozzarella stick is frozen  (hopefully) it should slide out the container then put that in your egg and then flour it a little then put all that Hot Cheeto dust on that 
Put it in the “fryer” (which is your hot pot full of oil make sure to have like a spatula and what not or tongs) then drop that in there make sure it deep fries a little then see if it’s cooked not burn then (I recommend looking up a YouTube video to know how long deep fried food is cooked and all) then when thats done put the nacho cheese sauce in a corner then cut the corner drizzle it on the deep fried food and WALA it’s done 😋😂

Edit: I would recommend to look up the recipe online cause there is people who I believe made this if I remember but any who make sure you get measurements right and all and I think your set so enjoy 😂👌🏼
